name: STATUS OF LIBRARY
data: College library has around 20,000 books. It subscribes 45 printed journals, 28 Magazines and 04 E-journals. The Reference Section has 3000 titles of reference books. Library also subscribes to many Newspapers .

name: Library Timing
data: The Library is open through out the year except on public holiday The Library functions from 9:00 A.M. to 5:30 P.M. Any change in these timings is notified on the notice board.
